        <xsd:element name="ShowBOM" type="ShowBOMType" id="oagis-id-39ef8a1c46d9431e849e9a249310e13c">
                <xsd:annotation>
                        <xsd:documentation source="http://www.openapplications.org/oagis/10">The purpose of the ShowBOM is to supply Item Bill of Material information to another business application module.  This BOD may also be initiated by the sending system upon some event occurring.

